<paragraph id="57403F59FF8FFF81FCD9CF566A4CFCF5" blockId="13.[813,1419,780,838]" pageId="13" pageNumber="196">
<emphasis id="658BE34BFF8FFF81FCD9CF566D6CFC97" bold="true" box="[813,1116,780,804]" pageId="13" pageNumber="196">Distribution and habitat.</emphasis>
Neotropical. Epiphytic in forests.
</paragraph>
